ARP in an Asynchronous Transfer Mode (ATM) network environment
configured as a Logical IP Subnetwork (LIS).",
URL="ftp://ftp.isi.edu/in-notes/rfc2225.txt",
}

@TECHREPORT{RFC-2224,
