Services Model. Comments should be made to the Integrated Services
Working Group, intserv@isi.edu.},
URL="ftp://ftp.isi.edu/in-notes/rfc2214.txt",
}

@TECHREPORT{RFC-2213,
AUTHOR="Baker, F. and Krawczyk, J. and Sastry, A.",
TITLE="Integrated Services Management Information Base using {SMIv2}",
TYPE="Request for Comments (Proposed Standard)",
INSTITUTION="Internet Engineering Task Force",
NUMBER=2213,
PAGES=21,
